                  </persName>, was indicted for<rs id="t18620407-492-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18620407-492-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18620407-492-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> uttering counterfeit coin.</rs>
